◆ load_kart_texture()

void load_kart_texture ( Player * player,
s8 playerId,
s8 arg2,
s8 arg3,
s8 arg4 )

Place DMA mio0 compressed character textures in a buffer. Later, this data becomes decompressed.

The player struct tracks the texture indices to load.

Parameters
player
playerIdPlayer ID.
arg2Rom buffer index appears to always be 0-3. Sometimes subtracted by 2.
arg3Second buffer index appears to always be 0-3.
arg4First buffer index always zero.
